- {id} is replaced automatically with the Token Identifier (groupID)
- For MGT tokens, these fields are required: ticker, name, chain, creator, description, attributes_url
- The hash is calculated over the text representation of the json string as written by UniValue (2 spaces tab, space after colon)
- The hash is stored on-chain
- The signature is calculated over the hash
- The signature is stored in the dynamic attributes file

